snippet.title: The Premier League is now on Sorare
snippet.description:
So, you want to manage your own Premier League club? 

Now you can on Sorare. Build your team, climb the ranks, and compete for big rewards - just like a real football club owner. 

Play now: https://go.sorare.com/ypjxp
